    "visibility_markdown": "## M-1 Outcomes\n\nObservational — settlement tracking; registered verdict metric is excess CLV.\nOutcome denominator basis: PA-valid settled player-market rows only; zero-PA and absent-boxscore rows are VOID.\nRetroactive-grading note: CLV sign is rendered from captured closes where available; this is report visibility only.\n\n### 2026-07-22 settlements\n\n| Market | Picks | Hits | Hit rate | Avg implied prob at pick |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| Doubles | 50 | 5 | 10.0% | 18.6% |\n| Hits | 73 | 43 | 58.9% | 57.6% |\n| HR | 44 | 8 | 18.2% | 15.3% |\n| Total bases | 86 | 38 | 44.2% | 45.8% |\n\nHR subgroup (secondary only; no HR-specific verdict): matched-close coverage=42/44 (95.5%); unmatched=2.\n\n#### CLV-sign split\n\n| Market | CLV bucket | Picks | Hits | Hit rate |\n|---|---|---|---|---|\n| Doubles | negative/flat CLV | 32 | 5 | 15.6% |\n| Doubles | positive CLV | 17 | 0 | 0.0% |\n| Hits | negative/flat CLV | 46 | 26 | 56.5% |\n| Hits | positive CLV | 27 | 17 | 63.0% |\n| HR | negative/flat CLV | 19 | 4 | 21.1% |\n| HR | positive CLV | 23 | 4 | 17.4% |\n| Total bases | negative/flat CLV | 50 | 24 | 48.0% |\n| Total bases | positive CLV | 35 | 14 | 40.0% |\n\nPositive-CLV-and-hit names: A.J. Ewing — Hits 0.5 @ Bally Bet; Brett Baty — Hits 0.5 @ DraftKings; CJ Abrams — Hits 1.5 @ Bally Bet; Dillon Dingler — Hits 0.5 @ theScore Bet; Dominic Canzone — Hits 0.5 @ theScore Bet; Dylan Crews — Hits 1.5 @ BetMGM; Francisco Lindor — Hits 0.5 @ Bally Bet; Freddie Freeman — Hits 0.5 @ DraftKings; Freddie Freeman — Hits 1.5 @ BetOnline.ag; Josh Bell — Hits 0.5 @ theScore Bet; Justin Foscue — Hits 0.5 @ Bally Bet; Kerry Carpenter — Hits 0.5 @ DraftKings; Kody Clemens — Hits 0.5 @ BetMGM; Luke Raley — Hits 0.5 @ Hard Rock Bet (OH); Royce Lewis — Hits 0.5 @ DraftKings; Spencer Torkelson — Hits 0.5 @ DraftKings; Trent Grisham — Hits 0.5 @ BetMGM; Brett Baty — HR 0.5 @ Hard Rock Bet (OH); Dalton Rushing — HR 0.5 @ betPARX; Sal Stewart — HR 0.5 @ BetR